@ManevilleF not happening on my machine.

<img width="1392" alt="Screenshot 2024-09-04 at 18 14 18" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e46fac6d-897e-493e-893a-7556da791110">

what specs can you reproduce this on?

The problem is just the linear sampling. There shouldn't be any artifacts if the texture is loaded with:
```
let image = asset_server.load_with_settings(
        "textures/fantasy_ui_borders/panel-border-010.png",
        |settings: &mut ImageLoaderSettings| {
            settings.sampler = ImageSampler::nearest();
        },
    );
```
